---
title: OpenClaw 아키텍처
---
graph TB
    subgraph channels["메시징 채널"]
        CH1[WhatsApp]
        CH2[Telegram]
        CH3[Slack]
        CH4[Discord]
        CH5[Signal]
        CH6[iMessage]
        CH7[웹챗]
    end

    subgraph gateway["OpenClaw Gateway (ws://127.0.0.1:18789)"]
        SM[세션 관리]
        CR[채널 라우팅]
        TR[툴 레지스트리]
        EB[이벤트 버스]
        SEC[보안 관문<br/>페어링 모드]
    end

    subgraph agents["에이전트 런타임"]
        A1[개인 비서<br/>SOUL: personal.md]
        A2[DevOps Bot<br/>SOUL: devops.md]
        A3[커뮤니티 관리<br/>SOUL: mod.md]
    end

    subgraph llm["LLM 백엔드"]
        L1[Claude]
        L2[GPT]
        L3[DeepSeek]
    end

    subgraph tools["도구"]
        T1[파일 시스템]
        T2[셸 명령]
        T3[웹 브라우저]
        T4[API 호출]
        T5[이메일]
    end

    CH1 & CH2 & CH3 & CH4 & CH5 & CH6 & CH7 --> gateway
    gateway --> agents
    agents --> llm
    agents --> tools

    style gateway fill:#2d3436,color:#fff
    style channels fill:#e8f4fd,stroke:#2196F3
    style agents fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#FF9800
    style llm fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#4CAF50
    style tools fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#E91E63
